  "body": "\r\nI believe it would be simpler and more intuitive to keep the gossip logic together in network/gossip. The handlers can be kept in a separate class to not pollute `Eth2Gossipsub` too much.\r\n\r\nThe current interface of start() and stop() is confusing and would be more accurate to use\r\n```ts\r\n.subscribeCoreTopics()\r\n.unsubscribeCoreTopics()\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
